cu.explanation_en: Setting the second integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the physical layer log level to an invalid enum 'invalid' will cause logging configuration errors and prevent the DU from starting with proper physical layer logging.
du.explanation_zh: 將物理層日誌級別設定為無效的枚舉值 'invalid'，會導致日誌配置錯誤，並阻止 DU 以適當的物理層日誌啟動。
